{"tid":2187300,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"2名警員早前涉參與非法賭博被捕 1獲釋1正式被控 明日上午提堂","createTime":"2020-09-03T14:01:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-03T14:39:05.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"7af203676113db691459fdcbdb20ed9fc640c91f","tid":2187300,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T14:01:39.000Z","msg":"屯門警區特別職務隊，於5月4日晚上11時許，進行打擊非法賭博行動，突擊搜查屯門建泰街一個單位，搗破一個非法賭博場所。行動中，警員拘捕28男8女(15歲至55歲)，當中2名分別姓潘(52歲)及姓陳(33歲)男子，更被發現為休班警員。<br />\n<br />\n屯門警區重案組其後接手調查案件，經進一步調查及徵詢法律意見後，由於沒有足夠證據對姓陳提出檢控，他已獲無條件釋放。而姓潘男子則已被控以一項「協助管理賭場」罪，案件將於明日(4日)上午在屯門裁判法院提堂。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，涉事的2名休班警務人員，分別駐守屯門警區巡邏小隊及大埔警區刑事調查隊，他們在事後已被停職。而涉事現場約1000平方呎，內有多個房間，包括麻雀房、桌球室，牌九室等，外表以party room（派對室）作包裝，警方於當日現場亦檢獲萬多元現金及籌碼。<br />\n<br />\nSOURCE: 東網"},{"pid":"8f63725314c0942de303848079c5ae5842a87168","tid":2187300,"uid":219010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T14:02:06.000Z","msg":"竟然無撤控<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49ccfd8e97ec01dc02cef2cb0ebd299d5c9baac4","tid":2187300,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f63725314c0942de303848079c5ae5842a87168","tid":2187300,"uid":219010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T14:02:06.000Z","msg":"竟然無撤控<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T14:02:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b0853033661ecf1dd2bfd7bfe186550ab9cd841","tid":2187300,"uid":224533,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"rep